Class Modifiers

  • java.lang.Object
    • asteroid.Modifiers
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    groovyjarjarasm.asm.Opcodes
    public class Modifiers
extends Object
implements groovyjarjarasm.asm.Opcodes
    This class acts as a proxy to access modifier codes found at Opcodes. Normally you should access them through A with the ACC key. E.g: 
         
 myNode.setModifiers(A.ACC.ACC_PUBLIC);
    Since:
    0.1.0
